00:06:29.270 --> 00:06:36.830
So claim one-- so
this is regarding

00:06:36.830 --> 00:06:39.900
the structural Feynman diagrams.

00:06:39.900 --> 00:06:48.350
So remember, the example
theory we conceded last time

