00:09:24.160 --> 00:09:26.230
and torus would not be enough.

00:09:26.230 --> 00:09:29.020
You would need, say, a genus
2 surface or higher genus

00:09:29.020 --> 00:09:29.520
surface.

00:09:34.640 --> 00:09:38.290
So you can easily
convince yourself

00:09:38.290 --> 00:09:44.890
