of disconnected regions

00:12:01.010 --> 00:12:02.570
In the diagram.

00:12:02.570 --> 00:12:10.660
And that number is the power of
n coming from the contracting

00:12:10.660 --> 00:12:12.180
propagators.

00:12:12.180 --> 00:12:16.290
So this claim is
also self-evident

00:12:16.290 --> 00:12:20.790
because each power of n comes
from a single connected line.

00:12:20.790 --> 00:12:22.840
And essentially, a
single connected line

00:12:22.840 --> 00:12:26.830
will be circles some face and
so the number of independents

00:12:26.830 --> 00:12:29.350
